Title: Emptiness formation probability of the XXZ spin-1/2 Heisenberg chain at  Delta=1/2
Authors: N. Kitanine and J. M. Maillet and N. A. Slavnov and V. Terras
Abstract: Using a multiple integral representation for the correlation functions, we compute the emptiness formation probability of the XXZ spin-1/2 Heisenberg chain at anisotropy Delta=1/2. We prove it is expressed in term of the number of alternating sign matrices.
